title: music/music related logos
content:
I am curious to know if any of you know studios or examples of either music stores (retail, instrument, etc) or musical products (instruments, etc) logotypes that are out there in people's online portfolios that I can take a look at. I've been searching for some but just come up with the regulars: sam goody, guitarcenter, musicians friend... but I'm looking for different ones, that are designed more meticulously. Anyone got anything out there for me to look at?

Thanks!
author: bxfl
